  <name>InkCut</name>
  <summary>Open-source 2D plotting and cuting software</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      An open source application for controlling 2D plotters, cutters,
      engravers, and CNC machines.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Graphic manipulation (Rotation, scaling, mirroring)</li>
      <li>Copy generation and layout</li>
      <li>Weedlines</li>
      <li>Inkscape integration</li>
      <li>Device control panel</li>
      <li>Job history list</li>
      <li>Live plot status</li>
      <li>Pause, resume, and abort jobs mid way</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
